                    "Detail": "<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"898a9f384da94451b75f77d0201ba559\");'><span id='898a9f384da94451b75f77d0201ba559_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年</a>，39岁</div><div id='898a9f384da94451b75f77d0201ba559' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年10月</a>　在长安，任李密府文学参军。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c558ebe188f04e769880a5a3987fab52\");'><span id='c558ebe188f04e769880a5a3987fab52_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>，42岁</div><div id='c558ebe188f04e769880a5a3987fab52' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>　入东宫。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e64477a9fb6c4057b74b7c36d3e39f2b\");'><span id='e64477a9fb6c4057b74b7c36d3e39f2b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年</a>，43岁</div><div id='e64477a9fb6c4057b74b7c36d3e39f2b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年</a>　在长安。任太子洗马。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7949f09d030d4ed580a301d1189909f1\");'><span id='7949f09d030d4ed580a301d1189909f1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=623&endYear=626')\">623-626年</a>，44-47岁</div><div id='7949f09d030d4ed580a301d1189909f1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=623&endYear=623')\">623年</a>　在长安。任太子洗马。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《赏旧左右议》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=624&endYear=625')\">624-625年</a>　在长安。任太子洗马。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年4月</a>　在长安。任詹事主簿。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7643a7c4fe8a46308b9e466bbe72a205\");'><span id='7643a7c4fe8a46308b9e466bbe72a205_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=637')\">626-637年</a>，47-58岁</div><div id='7643a7c4fe8a46308b9e466bbe72a205' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年9月</a>　在京任谏议大夫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年11月</a>　迁给事中，谏诏免租赋。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谏诏免租赋又令输纳疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=627&endYear=627')\">627年6月</a>　拜尚书右丞相。置宅东都劝善坊。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=628&endYear=628')\">628年</a>　与王圭上表请为李建成送葬。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《请陪送葬建成元吉表》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=629&endYear=629')\">629年</a>　在长安任秘书监。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=630&endYear=630')\">630年</a>　进言仁义，收聚石经。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=631&endYear=631')\">631年9月27日</a>　上所撰《群书治要》，太宗手诏答之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《群书治要序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=632&endYear=632')\">632年4月</a>　奉敕撰《九成宫醴泉铭》<span class='label'>作品：</span>《九成宫醴泉碑铭》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年1月</a>　奉命与虞世南等改制《破阵乐》歌词。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年6月</a>　与房玄龄游戴胄卒地，数为之流涕。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年</a>　奉命作《自古诸侯王善恶录》（今已佚，仅存序）<span class='label'>作品：</span>《诸王善恶录序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年</a>　追赠其父为定州刺史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=634&endYear=634')\">634年</a>　得太宗赞赏孜孜辅弼之功。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=635&endYear=635')\">635年</a>　欲拜右仆射，魏征固辞之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=636&endYear=636')\">636年1月</a>　与房玄龄等上所撰五代史。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《隋书·文学传序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=636&endYear=636')\">636年</a>　加左光禄大夫，进封郑国公。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>　上疏论君子小人。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《论君子小人疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>　上论时政第一、二、三、四疏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>　上疏论理狱与纳谏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《理狱听谏疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>　于洛阳西苑积翠池宴会赋《西汉》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f62838e0af054a63a804a134c8e36b56\");'><span id='f62838e0af054a63a804a134c8e36b56_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=643')\">638-643年</a>，59-64岁</div><div id='f62838e0af054a63a804a134c8e36b56' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年2月</a>　从太宗返京。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=639&endYear=639')\">639年5月</a>　上“十渐疏”<span class='label'>作品：</span>《十渐疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=639&endYear=639')\">639年</a>　参与整理御府所藏王羲之等书法作品。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=640&endYear=640')\">640年5月</a>　上所撰《类礼》二十卷。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=640&endYear=640')\">640年</a>　上疏论任臣之弊、御臣之弊。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《论御臣之疏》《论治道疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=641&endYear=641')\">641年7月</a>　谏于西域市马。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谏遣使市马疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=641&endYear=641')\">641年10月</a>　与高士廉等撰成《文思博要》一千二百卷。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=642&endYear=642')\">642年7月</a>　卧病，太宗手诏问疾，魏征上四奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《答太宗手诏疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=642&endYear=642')\">642年</a>　得赐庄田于澄城县，子孙居住，称郑公庄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=643&endYear=643')\">643年1月</a>　正月卒。临终草遗表讽谏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《遗表稿》<br /></div>"
